      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of care that meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been meticulously preserved. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber and documented pedigree.",
