    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's basically brand new and has been pampered since day one. Not a single scratch or dent anywhere\u2014it's in absolutely perfect condition! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
