      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2017 Shelby GT350, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the 5.2L Voodoo V8, utilizing a flat-plane crankshaft for reduced reciprocating mass and a staggering 8,250 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Tremec TR-3160 6-speed manual and a Torsen limited-slip differential with 3.73 gearing. Handling is optimized via the MagneRide Damping System, providing real-time adjustments to lateral load and pitch. Braking performance is handled by Brembo six-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously kept with no track history, this vehicle retains its factory tolerances and showroom-quality finish.",
